Commentary: Maiden Test wicket for Shadab. He pumps his fist and lets out a big roar. The feline Younis claims another sharp, low catch. This was the perfectly pitched legbreak, spins away outside off, and drags Dowrich forward. He prods with an angled bat, does not cover the line, and nicks it to slip.
